imdb.plot outline: Nate McClintock and Dana Simmons are two LAPD detectives working on a sex-trafficking case with Russian Mob involvement. With an array of under-cover officers poised to make an arrest, the two detectives struggle against the clock to obtain crucial information from Mickie Sanchez, a local prostitute who unknowingly holds the key to thwart the imminent illegal shipment of precious human cargo.

plot: Two detectives interrogate a prostitute for critical information that could unveil an international under-aged sex traffic scandal.::Rene Michelle Aranda
